title: Which Teams Are Actually Good? A Definitive List | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
With the NFL draft complete, 2020 rosters taking shape, and teams starting to gain hope, Kevin is joined by Eric Eager and George Chahrouri of 'Pro Football Focus' to run through every team in the NFL and answer the question: How many teams in the NFL are actually good?

Host: Kevin Clark
Guests: Eric Eager and George Chahrouri
